{"tid":2081831,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[BLM]Macy‘s 聲明澄清，前排俾打嘅白人係無辜","createTime":"2020-06-27T13:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T14:39:34.000Z","uid":201949,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"78287bff72b479a3316caa70ee921f4301576bc7","tid":2081831,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:55:22.000Z","msg":"原來俾人打嘅白人當時內部通話緊，因為Macy&rsquo;s公司政策所以被錄音。Macy&rsquo;s翻查紀錄後澄清受害人，當時嘅攻擊係無中生有。Macy&rsquo;s 正在同相關部門合作調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe man who was attacked was on an internal store call, which was recorded per company policy, and there is no recording of the employee using a racial slur.<br />\n<br />\nMacy's released a statement that read:<br />\n<br />\n&quot;We are deeply saddened about the incident that took place on Monday at Macy&rsquo;s Genesee Valley as the safety of Macy&rsquo;s customers and colleagues is our top priority. Violence in the workplace of any kind is unacceptable. <span style=\"color: red;\">All the materials from the evening have been reviewed and it is clear that the attack was unprovoked.</span>We are working closely with local authorities on this investigation, and will defer any further comments about the case to them per policy.<br />\n<br />\n汁：<a href=\"https://www.google.co.jp/amp/s/amp.thepostmillennial.com/brutal-macys-assault-unprovoked\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.jp%2Famp%2Fs%2Famp.thepostmillennial.com%2Fbrutal-macys-assault-unprovoked&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=de332167\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.co.jp/amp/s/amp.thepostmillennial.com/brutal-macys-assault-unprovoked</a>"},{"pid":"11694e8e2691715e8cdfb5881b8ac1cc8a4e409d","tid":2081831,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:56:56.000Z","msg":"左膠日報<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8465239/amp/Michigan-man-18-charged-assault-attack-white-Macys-employee.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-8465239%2Famp%2FMichigan-man-18-charged-assault-attack-white-Macys-employee.html&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=c1b1e672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8465239/amp/Michigan-man-18-charged-assault-attack-white-Macys-employee.html</a>"},{"pid":"ecaf395be27c1c08d638cd50c036af6b055c6184","tid":2081831,"uid":201949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:02:48.000Z","msg":"我就從來都唔屌左膠唔屌平權嘅，我甚至支持平權運動。<br />\n但要屌一眾媒體double standard，早排吹到話人哋講n word就日日頭版，而家公司澄清咗係老屈就細細聲咁報，根本就肋長緊黑人至上同逆向歧視。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/anncoulter/status/1275107449368911875?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fanncoulter%2Fstatus%2F1275107449368911875%3Fs%3D21&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=3556a421\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fanncoulter%2Fstatus%2F1275107449368911875%3Fs%3D21&h=700f2670\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/anncoulter/status/1275107449368911875?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"36f31fa5780a332eeb98a5315cb8de680e0c0697","tid":2081831,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:03:30.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461e1f15629f667ba86349d7090847a2609a4b76","tid":2081831,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:04:17.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"8801b6aa73e0322a47608c504b3e8236dd35f84a","tid":2081831,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:04:48.000Z","msg":"再自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08126b03582867ee6b606d331a3f4f7c065df1c","tid":2081831,"uid":337826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ecaf395be27c1c08d638cd50c036af6b055c6184","tid":208183